{"id": "1217312623465332756", "channel_id": "1216430569181941920", "type": 0, "author_id": "485414453152841749", "author_name": "wodebaobaoxiaodangaovi", "author_bot": false, "content": "今天同樣使用男蜘蛛，艾繼斯會一直增加手牌費用，在黑印和刻印不能正常的使用情況下很難抵銷這個負面效果", "timestamp": "2024-03-13T03:25:46.009000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1216430569181941920", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "阿格里帕實戰心得分享。輕鬆主宰幻夢深潛滿分", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778", "1211882178007408651", "1174179734373019748"]}
